item.description:
Klemens Franz (born April, 17 1979 in Graz, Austria) is a game artist from Austria.

Notable games include:

  • 2007 Agricola
  • 2008 Le Havre
  • 2009 1853 (Lookout Games Edition)
  • 2009 Agricola: Farmers of the Moor
  • 2009 At the Gates of Loyang
  • 2010 Luna
  • 2010 Merkator
  • 2010 The Mines of Zavandor
  • 2010 Bangkok Klongs
  • 2010 Poseidon
  • 2011 PAX
  • 2011 Walnut Grove
  • 2011 The Gnomes of Zavandor
  • 2011 Ora et Labora
  • 2011 Pergamon
  • 2012 Agricola: All Creatures Big and Small
  • 2012 Le Havre: The Inland Port
  • 2013 Bremerhaven
  • 2013 Caverna: The Cave Farmers
  • 2014 Orléans
  • 2015 Grand Austria Hotel
  • 2015 Isle of Skye: From Chieftain to King
  • 2015 Oh My Goods!
  • 2017 Clans of Caledonia
  • 2017 The Cousins' War
  • 2019 Expedition to Newdale
  • 2020 Glasgow
  • 2021 Boonlake
